snippet.title: Gears 5 - Official Horde Trailer
snippet.description:
#Gears5 Horde is back and better than ever!

Build a team of Heroes with unique Ultimates (including Jackbot!) and take on the most dynamic Horde experience to date. 

#Gears5 launches on September 10th. Get Xbox Game Pass Ultimate or the Ultimate Edition to play 4 days early on September 6th.
